ICS 156: Networking Lab 1.8.3 The MAC: Based on CSMA/CD nA broadcast bus - stations transmit in both directions nStations sense the channel before they transmit nWhen channel is sensed idle they transmit nStations listen while transmitting nTwo stations or more could start transmission at approx. the same time -> a collision results